column1: WNPF SINGLE LIFT NATIONAL EQUIPPED CHAMPIONSHIPS
*- WNPF WORLD RECORD, SP-SINGLE PLY LIFTER
TEAM CHAMPS- POWERLIFTING (EPHRATA REC), BENCH PRESS- TEAM REPUBLIC OF GEORGIA
MATT NOLAN, RICHARD AMBROSE, DAVE WILSON, CHUCK RACE, RON HASKAPER, DAN ST.FLEUR, GIORGI MESABLISHVILI

SEVERAL LIFTERS WERE TESTED AND THE RESULTS ARE PENDING WHICH COULD CHANGE SOME PLACINGS IN THIS CONTEST OR IT MAY NOT. THANKS TO THE WNPF STAFF FOR ALL OF THEIR HELP AND THANKS TO THE CHERRING SECTION 102 STRONG THAT CAME OUT AND CHEERED FOR ALL OF THE LIFTERS. WE HAD LIFTERS THAT TRAVELED FROM THE REPUBLIC OF GEORGIA AND FROM GUATEMALA TO ATTEND THIS MEET. A BIG THANK YOU TO THOSE LIFTERS FOR ATTENDING THIS CHAMPIONSHIP.
